comments: This contract is a call-up against a Public Works and Government Services Canada procurement tool/This contract is a multi-year contract./This contract is to undertake the preparation of tender documents (drawings and specifications) for the construction/rehabilitation of Lock building #34 (Fenelon Falls) and Lock building #43 (Swift Rapids, Ontario) and to provide resident services for construction and contract administration services during the demolition and construction/rehabilitation of the two lock buildings
